## 🚀 Features

- View list of Afghan proverbs
- Filter by keyword (search)
- Display random proverb
- Add new proverb
- Edit existing proverbs
- Delete proverbs
- Styled with Bootstrap RTL
- Multi-language fields (Dari, Pashto, English)

---

## 🧰 Technologies Used

- Backend: Node.js, Express, FileSystem, REST API
- Frontend: EJS Templates, Bootstrap 5, Vanilla JS, Axios
- Deploy: Render (Free Hosting)

